*pekwm-0.1.7 (20 Sep 2008)

  20 Sep 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +pekwm-0.1.7.ebuild:
  Version bump. Drop no longer needed gcc-4.3 patch. Update SRC_URI.

  24 Apr 2008; David Shakaryan <omp@gentoo.org>
  +files/pekwm-0.1.6-gcc-4.3.patch, pekwm-0.1.6.ebuild:
  Compile with GCC 4.3; patch from Debian modified by Peter Alfredsen. (bug
  #218956)

  09 Sep 2007; Santiago M. Mola <coldwind@gentoo.org> pekwm-0.1.5.ebuild,
  pekwm-0.1.6.ebuild:
  Remove vim swap file which got into themes tarball. Bug #190264

  20 Aug 2007; Stuart Longland <redhatter@gentoo.org> pekwm-0.1.6.ebuild:
  Tested and working on MIPS.  Keyworded ~mips as per bug #114498.

